Package: signit
Type: Package
Title: Mutation signatures in individual tumours
Version: 1.0.1
Date: 2017-12-28
Author: Eric Y. Zhao
Maintainer: Eric Y. Zhao <eric@eyzhao.com>
Description: Infers mutation signatures using a Bayesian hierarchical model. Also jointly infers temporally distinct tumour subpopulations alongside their signatures.
